{
  "texts": [
    "These underpinnings carry relevance for the analysis of this technical paper (specifically regarding disinformation and public trust).",
    "Other scholars might make different analyses when factoring in local political communication practices and their recent evolution in local media markets.Consequently, there is more research and reporting on some cases than in others.",
    "For example, the US 2024 elections received more coverage than Bhutan's 2024 elections.",
    "The varying strength and size of the news media in different jurisdictions affects the reporting that this research was able to uncover.",
    "Generally, minority languages are less reported on-for example in the USA, most efforts are directed at detecting misinformation in English."
  ]
}